1. Download Dockerfile and runwebsrv.sh script
2. Build the docker image from the folder which contains the Dockerfile - docker build -t webserv-img .
3. Add the runwebsrv.sh script to your zsh:
   Open your ZSH config file, probably: touch ~/.zshrc
   Add alias, example : alias runwebsrv="/Users/mrizhakov/Desktop/Docker/runwebsrv.sh"
   Update the zsh settings: source ~/.zshrc
   ...
   Profit
   If you dont have zsh - get it !
